text:
Great vibes, great people, fantastic food and great craft beers.
12 taps on regular rotation, highlighting the best crafts from local and global brewers.
Come on Saturday and u will be jiving to the sweet plucking and tunes by Johan Lee.

The epitome of a super local joint. Super chill vibes and the food is excellent, not your usual cheap bar bites. Great for a casual date, family, or with friends, and even just for a solo beer. Staff are super chill and friendly. A great standout in this otherwise quite dull neighbourhood. 10/10 would recommend. Pet friendly as well!
Great place with great vibes. Amazing staff , friendly faces. Food is great too and they have amazing member deals.
My favourite bar that I hang out at. Friendly staff, great beers and food.

Legit all the food we ordered were delicious.
Tried 2 of the beers on tap, they were ok but not great. The atmosphere and the really good food make it overall really solid. Hope they find another place to lease as they are closing soon at serene center.
